thread.title: T-Wolves' Kris Dunn balls out with between-the-legs assist against Rockets
thread.title_full: T-Wolves' Kris Dunn balls out with between-the-legs assist against Rockets

author: Zac Al-Khateeb (zac.alkhateeb@sportingnews.com)
title: T-Wolves' Kris Dunn balls out with between-the-legs assist against Rockets
text:
42am  42am EST Dunn pulled out the ole' razzle-dazzle out for this assist. Kris Dunn (Getty Images) 
Updated at 12:42  42 a.m. ET 
Kris Dunn showed that form and function don't have to come at the expense of style Saturday against the Rockets. 
The Timberwolves point guard pulled out the ole' razzle-dazzle with a no look, between-the-legs assist to Karl-Anthony Towns, who finished the play by driving the lane and scoring with a layup.
